{
  "texts": [
    "They used intermediate compression to train the network and achieved good accuracy even in a high-loss environment.",
    "Even without training with extremely compressed videos, their approach is the key to achieving great accuracy.Suratkar et al. [47] developed a system for detecting fake videos that used a CNN architecture and the TL.",
    "Their approach used a CNN to collect features from each movie frame to build a binary classifier that can efficiently distinguish between real and altered videos.",
    "Their approach was tested on many deepfake films culled from diverse datasets.",
    "The findings demonstrated that using TL to develop a relatively robust model for deepfake detection is doable."
  ]
}